From the problem data:
- The initial value of Retained Earnings as of 2023-12-31 is 0.00
- The end value of Retained Earnings as of 2024-02-05 is 56497.85

This indicates that during this period, the company retained a profit of 56497.85 rather than distributing it to shareholders.
